= v0.1.2
- Markable.has_key? to avoid predicate side-effects on v[:mark] when the value is false
- Markable.add_marks also accepts a block to mimic add_n_vertices and ElementSet.add_marks
- EdgeSet forwards source= and target= to its elements, allowing bulk reconnection
- Digraph.to_dot_attributes made much more intelligent on typical array values

= v0.1.1
- Bug fix in dot generation
- Examples started and documentation improved
- Web site index generation using wlang

= v0.1.0
- Digraph implementation
- Predicate implementation
- Selection mechanism